<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>PSG College of Technology - Summer Internship</title>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 0;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #000;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      line-height: 1.35;
      width: 210mm;
      min-height: 297mm;
      padding: 12mm 16mm 10mm 16mm;
      background: #fff;
    }

    /* ── HEADER ── */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 11pt;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .header h2 {
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* ── DATE ── */
    .date-line {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      margin-top: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    /* ── BODY TEXT ── */
    p {
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      margin: 3px 0;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .justify {
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .from-block {
      margin: 3px 0 6px 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
    }

    .to-block {
      margin: 4px 0;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
    }

    .through-line {
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      margin: 3px 0 2px 0;
    }

    .dear-line {
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      margin: 2px 0;
    }

    .sub-line {
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      margin: 3px 0;
    }

    /* ── TABLE ── */
    table.main-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 6px 0 4px 0;
      font-size: 8.5pt;
    }
    table.main-table td,
    table.main-table th {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 4px 5px;
      vertical-align: middle;
      font-size: 8.5pt;
    }
    table.main-table th {
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }
    table.main-table .data-row td {
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    /* Mentor cell inner layout */
    .mentor-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .mentor-inner .mentor-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .mentor-inner .mentor-label {
      font-weight: bold;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    /* ── CGPA ── */
    .cgpa-line {
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      margin: 5px 0 3px 0;
    }

    /* ── UNDERTAKING LIST ── */
    ol.undertaking {
      margin: 3px 0 3px 16px;
      padding: 0;
    }
    ol.undertaking li {
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    /* ── SIGNATURE ── */
    .sig-right {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    /* ── SIGNATORY ROW ── */
    table.sig-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    table.sig-table td {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #000;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 3px;
      font-size: 8.8pt;
      width: 16.66%;
    }

    /* ── PRINCIPAL ── */
    .principal-block {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 10pt;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    /* ── NOTE ── */
    .note-section {
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 8.8pt;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }
    .note-grid {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .note-label-cell {
      display: table-cell;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 8.8pt;
      white-space: nowrap;
      padding-right: 6px;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    .note-content-cell {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: top;
      font-size: 8.8pt;
    }
    ol.note-list {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 16px;
    }
    ol.note-list li {
      font-size: 8.8pt;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="header">
    <h1>PSG COLLEGE OF TECHNOLOGY, COIMBATORE 641 004</h1>
    <h2>Permission and Undertaking for Summer Internship / Short Duration Internship</h2>
  </div>

  <!-- DATE -->
  <div class="date-line"><strong>Date:</strong> {{currentDate}}</div>

  <!-- FROM -->
  <p><strong>From</strong></p>
  <div class="from-block">
    {{#if student_name}}{{student_name}}<br>{{/if}}
    {{#if roll_number}}{{roll_number}}<br>{{/if}}
    {{#if programme}}{{programme}}, Department of {{department}}{{/if}}
  </div>

  <!-- TO -->
  <div class="to-block">
    To<br>
    The Principal<br>
    PSG College of Technology<br>
    Coimbatore - 641004
  </div>

  <!-- THROUGH -->
  <p class="through-line">Through: The Head of the Department, Department of
    {{#if department}}{{department}}{{else}}______________________________{{/if}}
  </p>
  <p class="dear-line">Dear Sir,</p>

  <!-- SUB -->
  <p class="sub-line"><strong>Sub:</strong> Undertaking while pursuing Internship/Project Work II in Industry / Institutions.</p>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <p class="justify">
    I wish to inform that I have been offered Summer Internship / Short Duration Internship in the organization, details
    of which are provided below. The activities carried out during this internship will be useful for my placement and
    final year project work.
  </p>

  <!-- TABLE -->
  <table class="main-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:24%;">Name &amp; Address of the Industry / Institution<br>(with Contact Details &amp; Mobile Number)</th>
        <th colspan="2" style="width:18%;">Internship Period</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:22%;">Name of Mentor / Guide<br>(Industry &amp; Department)</th>
        <th colspan="2" style="width:18%;">Duration for which <br>Attendance  needed </th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:10%;">Stipend<br>Receivable<br>(if any)</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:9%;">From (Date)</th>
        <th style="width:9%;">To (Date)</th>
        <th style="width:9%;">From</th>
        <th style="width:9%;">To</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr class="data-row">
        <td>
          {{#if company_name}}<strong>{{company_name}}</strong><br>{{/if}}
          {{#if company_address}}{{company_address}}<br>{{/if}}
          {{#if company_city}}{{company_city}}{{#if company_state}}, {{company_state}}{{/if}}<br>{{/if}}
          {{#if guide_contact}}{{guide_contact}}{{/if}}
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{start_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{end_date}}</td>
        <td>
          <div class="mentor-inner">
            <div class="mentor-row">
              <span class="mentor-label">Industry:</span>
              <span>{{#if guide_name_industry}}{{guide_name_industry}}{{else}}&mdash;{{/if}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mentor-row">
              <span class="mentor-label">Dept:</span>
              <span>{{#if guide_name_dept}}{{guide_name_dept}}{{else}}&mdash;{{/if}}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{start_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{end_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">
          {{#if stipend_amount}}&#8377; {{stipend_amount}}{{else}}Nil{{/if}}
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <!-- CGPA — filled via template variables -->
  <p class="cgpa-line">
    My CGPA up to Semester
    <strong>{{#if cgpa_semester}}{{cgpa_semester}}{{else}}_____{{/if}}</strong>
    is
    <strong>{{#if cgpa_value}}{{cgpa_value}}{{else}}_______{{/if}}</strong>
  </p>

  <!-- REQUEST -->
  <p class="justify">
    I request you to permit me to accept the offer of the above internship and provide attendance for the duration mentioned.
  </p>

  <!-- UNDERTAKING -->
  <p style="margin: 4px 0 2px 0;"><strong>I hereby undertake the following:</strong></p>

  <ol class="undertaking">
    <li>I will be regular and sincere in carrying out my internship at the above organization and I will obey the Rules and Regulations of the organization.</li>
    <li>I will obtain the attendance certificate and submit the same at the academic section within a week from the last date of my internship and also submit a copy of the internship report to the HoD.</li>
    <li>I will study on my own the syllabi covered in class during my internship.</li>
    <li>Further, after return from internship, I will also complete the assessment components (except CA Test 1 if total CA tests are three) and laboratory experiments missed during the internship period after regular class hours.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed the offer letter for internship.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed the parent's consent letter.</li>
  </ol>

  <!-- STUDENT SIGNATURE -->
  <div class="sig-right">(Signature of the Student)</div>

  <!-- SIGNATORIES -->
  <table class="sig-table">
    <tr>
      <td>Tutor</td>
      <td>Guide (Dept)</td>
      <td>Programme Co-ordinator</td>
      <td>HoD</td>
      <td>Dean (P&amp;T)</td>
      <td>Dean-Academic</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- PRINCIPAL -->
  <div class="principal-block">PRINCIPAL</div>

  <!-- NOTE -->
  <div class="note-section">
    <div class="note-grid">
      <div class="note-label-cell">NOTE:</div>
      <div class="note-content-cell">
        <ol class="note-list">
          <li>Original Form shall be submitted to <strong>Placement Office</strong> and photocopies to <strong>Academic Section</strong> and <strong>Head of the Department</strong>.</li>
          <li>If hostel accommodation is required during the vacation period, a separate request letter shall be submitted for the same.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
